title: Subjective Industrial/electro House tracks 2013
description:
As stated in the title It's subjective, these are my favorite tracks of 2013
(some of 2012 could have slipped in though)

All Tracks are 320Kbps 

(Accept for "Moska Ft Antoine Becks - Insane" which is the non shitty non-vocal version but is only 128kbps) If you like vocals the normal one is also included.

So Recap 102 Songs 320Kbps

Afrojack,Bassjackers,Deorro,D.V.&L.M.,Hardwell,martin Garrix,Nicky Romero,
Sander Van Doorn, Tony Romera,Blasterjaxx

just to name a few..
